# Static assets served by the standalone dev server (yarn dev) at "/".
# The full figure set (~78 MB of SVGs + thumbnails) is too heavy for git: copy it
# here locally for testing, but keep it out of the repo. A committed catalog.json
# and a small `fixtures/` sample set are allowed so the dev server works for
# everyone out of the box.
*
!.gitignore
!catalog.json
!fixtures/
